data.description: Welcome home! Located in the gated Lehi Crossing, this beautiful residence perfectly blends modern living and elegant charm. Nestled on a corner lot with 3 beds + Den, 2 baths, 2-car garage, & a well-manicured landscape. You'll LOVE the inviting open layout designed for effortless entertaining! Natural light filled the spaces, enhanced by designer paint and wood-look tile flooring w/carpet in all the right places. The kitchen offers built-in appliances, granite counters, ample cabinetry, a pantry, recessed & pendant lighting, and an island w/breakfast bar. Versatile den is ideal for an office! Main bedroom has an ensuite with dual sinks & a walk-in closet. Out the back, you have a covered patio, lush lawn, & well-laid pavers. NO neighbors as it backs to a common area! Don't miss this gem!
